{
  "uid": "rs-coalescing",
  "title": "ReactantServer / Coalescing & Batching",
  "tags": [
    "reactantserver",
    "coalescing",
    "batching"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-3h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "worker",
        "label": "Worker",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(worker_info, worker)",
          "refId": "worker"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to read this",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Coalescing factor** = requests merged per device dispatch (`worker_requests_served_total / worker_dispatch_total`), i.e. the average effective batch size. **Max batch** = largest size the model is compiled to coalesce to (`<=1` means no batch axis: it *cannot* be batched). **Fill** = coalescing / max batch. **device s/s** = device-seconds consumed per wall-second (1.0 = one full device), sort by it to find the heaviest models; **device/disp** is the per-execution device cost. Targeting: a model with high **device s/s** and **max batch <=1** is expensive yet non-batchable , a candidate to invest in making batchable; high device s/s with low **fill** is batchable but underused (raise the batch window or arrival concurrency). Aggregated over the selected time range and worker(s); covers every device-executing model, including meta sub-models."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Per-model device cost & coalescing (sorted by device usage)",
      "description": "Each model's device consumption alongside how well it batches. Default-sorted by device s/s (heaviest first); click any header to re-sort, e.g. by fill for batching headroom. A heavy model with max batch <=1 is the make-it-batchable candidate. Models with no dispatches in the range are excluded.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 13,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "filterable": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "model"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.width",
                "value": 360
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "device s/s"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "none"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 2
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-text"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "orange",
                      "value": 0.2
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 0.5
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "device/disp"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "s"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 3
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "disp/s"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "ops"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 2
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "coalescing"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "none"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 2
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "max batch"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "none"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "fill"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "percentunit"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background",
                  "mode": "gradient"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "orange",
                      "value": 0.5
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": 0.85
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [
          {
            "displayName": "device s/s",
            "desc": true
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(worker_requests_served_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) / clamp_min(sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])), 1e-9) and on (model) (sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) > 0)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max by (model) (worker_model_max_batch_size{worker=~\"$worker\"}) and on (model) (sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) > 0)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "D",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "(sum by (model) (rate(worker_requests_served_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) / clamp_min(sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])), 1e-9)) / clamp_min(max by (model) (worker_model_max_batch_size{worker=~\"$worker\"}), 1) and on (model) (sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) > 0)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "E",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(worker_compute_seconds_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) and on (model) (sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) > 0)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "F",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(worker_compute_seconds_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) / clamp_min(sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])), 1e-9) and on (model) (sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) > 0)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "merge",
          "options": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value #A": "disp/s",
              "Value #B": "coalescing",
              "Value #C": "max batch",
              "Value #D": "fill",
              "Value #E": "device s/s",
              "Value #F": "device/disp"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Most under-filled models (bottom 20 by fill)",
      "description": "The 20 coalescable models running furthest below their compiled max batch , the clearest batching-improvement candidates. Bars near 100% are already well-batched.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 17
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.5
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0.85
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "bottomk(20, (sum by (model) (rate(worker_requests_served_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])) / clamp_min(sum by (model) (rate(worker_dispatch_total{worker=~\"$worker\"}[$__range])), 1e-9)) / clamp_min(max by (model) (worker_model_max_batch_size{worker=~\"$worker\"}), 1) and on (model) (max by (model) (worker_model_max_batch_size{worker=~\"$worker\"}) > 1))",
          "format": "time_series",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "{{model}}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
